{"tid":2177181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家明：唔好再話做任何野係無用啦","createTime":"2020-08-27T14:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T17:07:52.000Z","uid":220066,"like":111,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"282337a79eb4675969e376787c9b82c7a02402cf","tid":2177181,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"17歲的勇氣<br />\n<br />\n最初見到「Lunch哥」David，沒太大好感，以為純粹搶Fo，不用腦一味衝的年輕人，現在回想，非常慚愧，竟用大人的成本世界，猜想17歲的初生之犢。<br />\n<br />\n今日，他保釋候審，記者咪兜面前，我看到的是勇氣。<br />\n<br />\n他向記者說，「政府想我畏懼，他越想我收聲，我越要繼續抗爭，唔會就咁放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n嗯，17歲的時候，你在做甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n不要再說做乜無用，著黑衫無用，遊行無用，罷工無用...<br />\n<br />\n最無用的，是說無用的人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/08/27/220232_90b4277d2285b17ae4090828a3696bc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F27%2F220232_90b4277d2285b17ae4090828a3696bc4.png&h=18a8c5ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0851f90b4f74ecdf0356aeb8f1d803b76821f61","tid":2177181,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e65afd3d5ab30e9205bad0816ab1743cddeb620b","tid":2177181,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90c5d89cca87d9448678b0c8fb30a4ba3b06cfe2","tid":2177181,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53020d64316f2c99e4ed6e3478fd12b620afc4b4","tid":2177181,"uid":288093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d73f65c2c25d3e7c4cfe7c54098ef12db2e514f","tid":2177181,"uid":72994,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"以佢為榜樣唔好放棄，唔好停止"},{"pid":"52bcd400ecb15cd957ac1556df784f10957debaf","tid":2177181,"uid":288093,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"乜